body.name: Yaheetech Home Office 47 Inch Writing Desk with Power Outlets and 2 USB Charging Ports for Studying, Gaming Table Computer Desk with Hutch and Bookshelf, Metal Frame Workstation for Office, Gray
features: 【Built-in Power Outlet】To ensure maximum efficiency this desk is fitted with a built-in power outlet, you’ll have ample space to charge all your items with ease. The 1500W power outlet with a 2m long cord, 2 ACs & 2 USB ports, a switch, and a hook & loop, adopts a three-plug and a double-insulated round wire, convenient and safe!

【Ample SIZE, Compact Storage】With a 55 x 120 cm (L x W) tabletop and a 74 cm high under space, you will have a large platform to deal with your work and ample space to get your legs cozily stretched. The vertically arranged storage above and below the tabletop releases your valuable working area while providing ample space for essential and display items.
【Floor Protective Foot Pads】To prevent unnecessary scratches on your floor during movement, this office desk comprises 4 protective foot pads. Do not forget to install them during assembly.

【Stylish Design for Wider Use】Unlike traditional office supplies, this industrial style piece features crisp lines with contrasting finishes; matt black metal frame with contrasting wooden shelving and table top pair effortlessly, exuding style. This computer desk will fit perfectly into various spaces with its modern and versatile design.

【Expanded Storage, Complete Working Area】Two storage areas include an elevated shelf and a frame under the tabletop. Items like books and decorations can have their residence, leaving the working area clear and organized.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 21, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Love this desk for my bedroom! Beautiful and sturdy overall. Assembly was straightforward for the most part, though going under to screw in the main table part was alittle nightmare-ish. Getting it to align and having the wrench keep knocking into the metal bars was kind of tedious and annoying. This is a very minor complaint though, the desk was worth the effort!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great size and durable!
reviews.reviewText: This desk is cute, takes up minimal space, and is sturdy! Love the color and it only took my husband about 30 minutes to put together. Definitely recommend. AMAZING for the price!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 15, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Updating review...After seller contacted me regarding the missing piece, they sent out a new desk. So excited. It was easy to put together, sturdy and if course adorable and I love having the outlet on the desk which makes it so easy to charge phone, use my glue stick gun and other stuff for creating my crafts.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A little short
reviews.reviewText: Great sturdy desk with pretty easy install, however it’s a lot shorter than expected. Overall though 5 stars!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 8, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Amazing desk for the price!!! It’s sturdy, relatively uncomplicated to put together (instructions are diagram only, but all the parts are numbered), and the color is very pretty! It’s not as heavy as I thought it would be either, which is great for getting it set up.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Very nice and sturdy desk
reviews.reviewText: The desk is nice and sturdy, but the directions doesn’t give a step by step explanation so putting it together is very time consuming.Once put together, the top of the desk is very spacious. The bookshelf is nice, but you might want to lay them down or book divider/holders. The very top is very nice for pictures, desk decor, sharper, etc. I will be using the desk for school/work so the space is much needed.I will be ordering this desk again for my wife soon.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 12, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Easy to put together.. daughter enjoys the outlet to plug in phone and lamp. Great quality. Would highly recommend

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 23, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Good price. Very sturdy. Fits perfect in my bedroom
